org.terrier.realtime.compression

Class MemBitSetBuffer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.terrier.realtime.compression.MemBitSetBuffer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Closeable, AutoCloseable, BitIn, BitOut

    public class MemBitSetBuffer
extends Object
implements BitOut, BitIn
    Buffer backed by a BitSet. Supports gamma and unary encoding of strictly positive integers.
    Since:
    4.0
